OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FA teacher accused of murdering an
OL,7,Fadopted baby told his partner: "Your
OL,8,Fson's in hospital. I strangled him", a
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FJamie Varley, 37, a minute later sent
OL,12,Fa second text to his boyfriend, John
OL,13,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, 32, saying:
OL,14,F"Jokes. Just give me a call when done."
OL,16,FThe defendants had adopted 13-month-
OL,17,Fold Preston Davey at their home in
OL,18,FBlackpool in April 2023, Preston Crown
OL,19,FCourt heard.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@cO]vD@AOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
