PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FVarley is accused of the murder of the
OL,7,Fchild and McGowan-Fazakerley of
OL,8,Fallowing the death of the child, with
OL,9,Fboth accused of sexual abuse, the
OL,10,Ftrial, now in its second week, has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FThe text messages were sent on July
OL,14,F10, just four days after Preston had
OL,15,Fbeen admitted to Blackpool Victoria
OL,16,FHospital for a third time, after
OL,17,Fearlier visits in May and June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
