PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FOn the morning of July 6 2023, Varley
OL,7,Ftook Preston to hospital with an
OL,8,Finjury to his elbow. He told hospital
OL,9,Fstaff he was lowering the baby into
OL,10,Fhis cot the night before when the
OL,11,Fchild jumped or kicked his feet and he
OL,12,Fheard a pop or click in his left elbow.
OL,14,FAn X-ray confirmed a small fracture
OL,15,Fand his arm was put in a cast.Later
OL,16,Fthe child's social worker, Amy
OL,17,FShepherdson, who had been in contact
OL,18,Fwith the hospital, texted Varley to
OL,19,Fsay:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,F"Just to reassure you they said they
OL,7,Fhad absolutely no concerns.
OL,9,F"U absolutely did the right thing."
OL,11,FMs Shepherdson visited their home
OL,12,Flater that day, noting that Preston
OL,13,Flooked pale and was not himself,
OL,14,Fadding: "He tried to smile several
OL,15,Ftimes but then this changed to a very
OL,16,Fsad face and a little cry."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUqD@cO]vD@IOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
