FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FJurors were also shown a text exchange
OL,7,Fbetween Varley and his friend, Tanya
OL,8,FTingle, telling her: "We did it we
OL,9,Fthink...not on purpose but caught him
OL,10,Fwhen falling."
OL,12,FA day later the family had a home
OL,13,Fvisit from Helen Magee, an independent
OL,14,Freviewer from Oldham social services.
OL,26,@pD@VOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
