PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FIn her report of the visit, apparently
OL,7,Faddressed to the baby, she wrote: "You
OL,8,Fwere happy there with both your
OL,9,Fdaddies. And this made me ponder a
OL,10,Flittle as to whether there was a
OL,11,Fproblem that I couldn't see. I decided
OL,12,Fthere wasn't an issue..."
OL,26,@oD@cOUtD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
