FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FDr Alberto Elbo, an orthopaedic
OL,7,Fsurgeon, treated Preston at the
OL,8,Ffracture clinic the following week,
OL,9,Fwhen Varley brought him in. Jurors
OL,10,Fwere shown notes from the meeting he
OL,11,Fhad dictated which said he was told
OL,12,Fthe injury to the arm was from Preston
OL,13,Fbeing placed and strapped in a car
OL,14,Fseat and nothing to do with a cot.
OL,16,FPeter Wright KC, prosecuting, asked Dr
OL,17,FElbo about this explanation involving
OL,18,Fa car seat.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FDr Elbo said: "That's what dad told
OL,7,Fme. What I understood from that day
OL,8,Fwas he was being strapped in his car
OL,9,Fseat. That's all I had in my mind when
OL,10,FI dictated that letter."
OL,12,FNick Johnson KC, defending Varley
OL,13,Fsuggested to the witness he had been
OL,14,Ftold the injury came about due to a
OL,15,F"cot" not a "car".
OL,17,F"I don't think so," Dr Elbo replied.
OL,26,@nD@OOUrD@XO]wD@AOUwD@EO]wD@MOUwD@QO]yD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@SO]
