PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FPreston was born on June 16 2022,
OL,7,Fimmediately taken into care by Oldham
OL,8,FCouncil, and placed with foster
OL,9,Fparents at five days old.
OL,11,FAfter undergoing an assessment and
OL,12,Ffamiliarisation process in early 2023
OL,13,Fhe was adopted and began living with
OL,14,Fthe defendants on April 1 at their
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FVarley took a year off work as head of
OL,7,Fyear and as a design and technology
OL,8,Fteacher at a local high school, South
OL,9,FShore Academy, to look after the
OL,10,Fchild, but struggled as a new parent
OL,11,Fwith a baby who frequently woke during
OL,12,Fthe night and with his partner working
OL,13,Flong hours, the court heard.
OL,15,FDuring the four months the baby was
OL,16,Funder their adoption he was allegedly
OL,17,Froutinely ill-treated, had indecent
OL,18,Fimages and videos taken of him, was
OL,19,Fsexually abused and physically
OL,20,Fassaulted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1777665953
OL,3,C'I strangled him': baby murder trial
OL,4,Chears of text messages
OL,6,FOn July 27 2023 Preston was again
OL,7,Fbrought in to the hospital by the
OL,8,Fdefendants, unconscious and in a state
OL,9,Fof cardiac arrest, and medics could
OL,10,Fnot revive him. Varley told police the
OL,11,Fchild accidentally drowned in a bath,
OL,12,Fbut this was inconsistent with the
OL,13,Fpost-mortem examination which
OL,14,Fdiscovered the child had suffered 40
OL,15,Ftraumatic injuries, the court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
